{
  "id": "RAW_124f4108",
  "title": "Vercel AI Gateway 零数据留存功能",
  "url": "https://vercel.com/blog/zdr-on-ai-gateway",
  "date": "2026-04-06 20:02:03",
  "author": "Jerilyn Zheng, Dan Fein",
  "siteName": "Vercel News",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div data-customer-story=\"false\" class=\"flex flex-col items-center justify-start gap-6 flex-initial article-module__9eLiuW__content\">\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">Building with multiple AI models means wrestling with fragmented data policies. With many different model providers, it's not just fragmented, it's just too much time spent on the wrong things.</p>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">You have to read through different terms of service, track which providers comply with your security requirements, and hope developers remember to configure opt-outs correctly on every request. What should be a straightforward policy becomes a manual, error-prone process because many providers do not offer Zero Data Retention (ZDR) by default.</p>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\"><a href=\"https://vercel.com/docs/ai-gateway\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_self\" data-track=\"true\" data-track-click-name=\"article_link\" data-track-click-value=\"https://vercel.com/docs/ai-gateway\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link no-underline link-module__Q1NRQq__highlight [&amp;_u]:no-underline\">AI Gateway</a> changes this by handling the negotiation and enforcement for you. Instead of managing policies provider by provider, you get the freedom to just build. AI Gateway ensures your data requirements are met automatically by only routing to providers where we have negotiated Zero Data Retention agreements. Models from OpenAI, Anthropic, Google, and more have ZDR providers available.</p>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">Today, we are expanding AI Gateway's compliance capabilities with team-wide Zero Data Retention (ZDR), letting you enforce strict data policies across your entire team without touching any code. Gateway compliance features now include team-wide ZDR from the dashboard, per-request ZDR for specific sensitive workflows, and explicit controls to disallow prompt training.</p>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">Toggle on in the <a href=\"https://vercel.com/d?to=%2F%5Bteam%5D%2F%7E%2Fai-gateway%2Fsettings\\&amp;title=AI+Gateway+Settings\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_self\" data-track=\"true\" data-track-click-name=\"article_link\" data-track-click-value=\"https://vercel.com/d?to=%2F%5Bteam%5D%2F%7E%2Fai-gateway%2Fsettings\\&amp;title=AI+Gateway+Settings\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link no-underline link-module__Q1NRQq__highlight [&amp;_u]:no-underline\">AI Gateway Dashboard Settings</a>, and all subsequent requests via AI Gateway will only route through ZDR-compliant providers.</p>\n   <div class=\"flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-4 max-w-none not-frist:mt-20 not-first:mb-10 mx-0 max-[600px]:max-w-none max-[600px]:px-7 max-[600px]:[li_&amp;]:pr-14 max-[600px]:[li_&amp;]:pl-0 max-[600px]:w-full max-[600px]:mt-12 max-[600px]:mb-6\">\n    <img data-version=\"v1\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"900\" height=\"418\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"image-module__ssnYEW__intrinsic image-module__ssnYEW__lightMode\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcset=\"https://vercel.com/vc-ap-vercel-marketing/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.vercel.com%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fcontentful%2Fimage%2Fe5382hct74si%2F1JLd8aVrsB0x0HfKGORORR%2F559c6909e9fb13e47bcdad5da4722560%2FCleanShot_2026-04-03_at_15.52.16_2x.png&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1x, https://vercel.com/vc-ap-vercel-marketing/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.vercel.com%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fcontentful%2Fimage%2Fe5382hct74si%2F1JLd8aVrsB0x0HfKGORORR%2F559c6909e9fb13e47bcdad5da4722560%2FCleanShot_2026-04-03_at_15.52.16_2x.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"https://vercel.com/vc-ap-vercel-marketing/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.vercel.com%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fcontentful%2Fimage%2Fe5382hct74si%2F1JLd8aVrsB0x0HfKGORORR%2F559c6909e9fb13e47bcdad5da4722560%2FCleanShot_2026-04-03_at_15.52.16_2x.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75\">\n   </div>\n   <h3 class=\"text-heading-20 lg:text-heading-24 font-semibold relative group w-full pt-8 text-module__fl7lUq__subheading\"><a class=\"flex items-center justify-center flex-col absolute left-0 bottom-0 mt-auto mb-auto w-8 h-8 rounded-full opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 -translate-x-3/4 group-hover:-translate-x-full delay-75 duration-300 transition-all text-gray-900 hover:text-gray-1000 hover:scale-110 focus-visible:-translate-x-full focus-visible:opacity-100 top-6 [#changelog-description_&amp;]:hidden\" href=\"#team-wide-zero-data-retention\" id=\"team-wide-zero-data-retention\" style=\"scroll-margin-top:90px\"> \n     <svg data-testid=\"geist-icon\" height=\"16\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"width:12px;height:12px;color:currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\">\n      <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M8.46968 1.46968C10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 -0.203923 14.5303 1.46968C16.2039 3.14329 16.2039 5.85674 14.5303 7.53034L12.0303 10.0303L10.9697 8.96968L13.4697 6.46968C14.5575 5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 13.4697 2.53034C12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 1.44252 9.53034 2.53034L7.03034 5.03034L5.96968 3.96968L8.46968 1.46968ZM11.5303 5.53034L5.53034 11.5303L4.46968 10.4697L10.4697 4.46968L11.5303 5.53034ZM1.46968 14.5303C3.14329 16.2039 5.85673 16.204 7.53034 14.5303L10.0303 12.0303L8.96968 10.9697L6.46968 13.4697C5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 14.5575 2.53034 13.4697C1.44252 12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 2.53034 9.53034L5.03034 7.03034L3.96968 5.96968L1.46968 8.46968C-0.203923 10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 1.46968 14.5303Z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path>\n     </svg> \n     <span class=\"sr-only\">Link to heading</span> \n    </a>Team-wide Zero Data Retention</h3>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">Team-wide ZDR is available for Pro and Enterprise teams. It applies to every request your team makes, requiring no code changes. This is ideal for teams that want controls with complete assurance that no one can modify or misapply restrictions.</p>\n   <h3 class=\"text-heading-20 lg:text-heading-24 font-semibold relative group w-full pt-8 text-module__fl7lUq__subheading\"><a class=\"flex items-center justify-center flex-col absolute left-0 bottom-0 mt-auto mb-auto w-8 h-8 rounded-full opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 -translate-x-3/4 group-hover:-translate-x-full delay-75 duration-300 transition-all text-gray-900 hover:text-gray-1000 hover:scale-110 focus-visible:-translate-x-full focus-visible:opacity-100 top-6 [#changelog-description_&amp;]:hidden\" href=\"#request-level-controls\" id=\"request-level-controls\" style=\"scroll-margin-top:90px\"> \n     <svg data-testid=\"geist-icon\" height=\"16\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"width:12px;height:12px;color:currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\">\n      <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M8.46968 1.46968C10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 -0.203923 14.5303 1.46968C16.2039 3.14329 16.2039 5.85674 14.5303 7.53034L12.0303 10.0303L10.9697 8.96968L13.4697 6.46968C14.5575 5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 13.4697 2.53034C12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 1.44252 9.53034 2.53034L7.03034 5.03034L5.96968 3.96968L8.46968 1.46968ZM11.5303 5.53034L5.53034 11.5303L4.46968 10.4697L10.4697 4.46968L11.5303 5.53034ZM1.46968 14.5303C3.14329 16.2039 5.85673 16.204 7.53034 14.5303L10.0303 12.0303L8.96968 10.9697L6.46968 13.4697C5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 14.5575 2.53034 13.4697C1.44252 12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 2.53034 9.53034L5.03034 7.03034L3.96968 5.96968L1.46968 8.46968C-0.203923 10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 1.46968 14.5303Z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path>\n     </svg> \n     <span class=\"sr-only\">Link to heading</span> \n    </a>Request-level controls</h3>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">Per-request ZDR lets you enforce data deletion on specific requests when only certain workflows handle sensitive data. This is useful when your app has proprietary information in certain queries but other requests are not as protected. You can enable request-level ZDR in all API formats supported by AI Gateway in the <a href=\"https://vercel.com/docs/ai-gateway/models-and-providers/provider-options\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_self\" data-track=\"true\" data-track-click-name=\"article_link\" data-track-click-value=\"https://vercel.com/docs/ai-gateway/models-and-providers/provider-options\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link no-underline link-module__Q1NRQq__highlight [&amp;_u]:no-underline\">provider options</a>.</p>\n   <div class=\"flex flex-col items-stretch justify-start gap-4 flex-initial blog-code-block-module__zaYDqW__wrapper\">\n    <div class=\"relative code-block-module__NOThwW__wrapper code-block-module__NOThwW__hideLineNumbers blog-code-block-module__zaYDqW__codeBlock\" data-geist-code-block=\"\">\n     <button aria-label=\"Copy code\" class=\"code-block-module__NOThwW__copyButton code-block-module__NOThwW__copyFloatingButton\" type=\"button\"></button>\n     <pre class=\"prism-code language-typescript code-block-module__NOThwW__pre\"><code class=\"code-block-module__NOThwW__code\" data-geist-code-block=\"true\"><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C3f5ccb57-L1\" data-highlighted=\"false\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token keyword\">type</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token plain\"> GatewayProviderOptions </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token keyword\">from</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token string\">'@ai-sdk/gateway'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C3f5ccb57-L2\" data-highlighted=\"false\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\"></span><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token plain\"> streamText </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token keyword\">from</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token string\">'ai'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C3f5ccb57-L3\" data-highlighted=\"false\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\" style=\"display:inline-block\">\n</span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C3f5ccb57-L4\" data-highlighted=\"false\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\"></span><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span><span class=\"token plain\"> result </span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token function\">streamText</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C3f5ccb57-L5\" data-highlighted=\"false\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">  model</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token string\">'anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.6'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C3f5ccb57-L6\" data-highlighted=\"false\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">  prompt</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token string\">'Analyze this sensitive business data and provide insights.'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C3f5ccb57-L7\" data-highlighted=\"false\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">  providerOptions</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C3f5ccb57-L8\" data-highlighted=\"false\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">    gateway</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C3f5ccb57-L9\" data-highlighted=\"true\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">      zeroDataRetention</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C3f5ccb57-L10\" data-highlighted=\"false\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">    </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token plain\"> satisfies GatewayProviderOptions</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C3f5ccb57-L11\" data-highlighted=\"false\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">  </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C3f5ccb57-L12\" data-highlighted=\"false\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\"></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></div></div></code></pre>\n    </div>\n    <p class=\"text-center text-copy-14 text-gray-900\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">Team-wide and per-request settings work together. If either is enabled, ZDR is enforced.</p>\n   <h3 class=\"text-heading-20 lg:text-heading-24 font-semibold relative group w-full pt-8 text-module__fl7lUq__subheading\"><a class=\"flex items-center justify-center flex-col absolute left-0 bottom-0 mt-auto mb-auto w-8 h-8 rounded-full opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 -translate-x-3/4 group-hover:-translate-x-full delay-75 duration-300 transition-all text-gray-900 hover:text-gray-1000 hover:scale-110 focus-visible:-translate-x-full focus-visible:opacity-100 top-6 [#changelog-description_&amp;]:hidden\" href=\"#disallow-prompt-training\" id=\"disallow-prompt-training\" style=\"scroll-margin-top:90px\"> \n     <svg data-testid=\"geist-icon\" height=\"16\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"width:12px;height:12px;color:currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\">\n      <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M8.46968 1.46968C10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 -0.203923 14.5303 1.46968C16.2039 3.14329 16.2039 5.85674 14.5303 7.53034L12.0303 10.0303L10.9697 8.96968L13.4697 6.46968C14.5575 5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 13.4697 2.53034C12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 1.44252 9.53034 2.53034L7.03034 5.03034L5.96968 3.96968L8.46968 1.46968ZM11.5303 5.53034L5.53034 11.5303L4.46968 10.4697L10.4697 4.46968L11.5303 5.53034ZM1.46968 14.5303C3.14329 16.2039 5.85673 16.204 7.53034 14.5303L10.0303 12.0303L8.96968 10.9697L6.46968 13.4697C5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 14.5575 2.53034 13.4697C1.44252 12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 2.53034 9.53034L5.03034 7.03034L3.96968 5.96968L1.46968 8.46968C-0.203923 10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 1.46968 14.5303Z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path>\n     </svg> \n     <span class=\"sr-only\">Link to heading</span> \n    </a>Disallow Prompt Training</h3>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">Disallow Prompt Training prevents providers from using your prompt data to train their models. This is a good default for any team sending proprietary code, internal documents, or business strategy through an LLM. This filter is available on the request-level.</p>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">ZDR is a superset of this control. If you enable ZDR, training opt-out is already covered.</p>\n   <div class=\"flex flex-col items-stretch justify-start gap-4 flex-initial blog-code-block-module__zaYDqW__wrapper\">\n    <div class=\"relative code-block-module__NOThwW__wrapper code-block-module__NOThwW__hideLineNumbers blog-code-block-module__zaYDqW__codeBlock\" data-geist-code-block=\"\">\n     <button aria-label=\"Copy code\" class=\"code-block-module__NOThwW__copyButton code-block-module__NOThwW__copyFloatingButton\" type=\"button\"></button>\n     <pre class=\"prism-code language-typescript code-block-module__NOThwW__pre\"><code class=\"code-block-module__NOThwW__code\" data-geist-code-block=\"true\"><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C7eb12b0b-L1\" data-highlighted=\"false\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token keyword\">type</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token plain\"> GatewayProviderOptions </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token keyword\">from</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token string\">'@ai-sdk/gateway'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C7eb12b0b-L2\" data-highlighted=\"false\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\"></span><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token plain\"> streamText </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token keyword\">from</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token string\">'ai'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C7eb12b0b-L3\" data-highlighted=\"false\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\" style=\"display:inline-block\">\n</span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C7eb12b0b-L4\" data-highlighted=\"false\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\"></span><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span><span class=\"token plain\"> result </span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token function\">streamText</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C7eb12b0b-L5\" data-highlighted=\"false\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">  model</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token string\">'anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.6'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C7eb12b0b-L6\" data-highlighted=\"false\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">  prompt</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token string\">'Analyze this proprietary business strategy.'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C7eb12b0b-L7\" data-highlighted=\"false\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">  providerOptions</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C7eb12b0b-L8\" data-highlighted=\"false\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">    gateway</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C7eb12b0b-L9\" data-highlighted=\"true\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">      disallowPromptTraining</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C7eb12b0b-L10\" data-highlighted=\"false\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">    </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token plain\"> satisfies GatewayProviderOptions</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C7eb12b0b-L11\" data-highlighted=\"false\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">  </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C7eb12b0b-L12\" data-highlighted=\"false\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\"></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></div></div></code></pre>\n    </div>\n    <p class=\"text-center text-copy-14 text-gray-900\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">Each response includes metadata showing which providers were considered and which were filtered out. This gives you an audit trail of how your data policies were enforced.</p>\n   <div class=\"flex flex-col items-stretch justify-start gap-4 flex-initial blog-code-block-module__zaYDqW__wrapper\">\n    <div class=\"relative code-block-module__NOThwW__wrapper code-block-module__NOThwW__hideLineNumbers blog-code-block-module__zaYDqW__codeBlock\" data-geist-code-block=\"\">\n     <button aria-label=\"Copy code\" class=\"code-block-module__NOThwW__copyButton code-block-module__NOThwW__copyFloatingButton\" type=\"button\"></button>\n     <pre class=\"prism-code language-json code-block-module__NOThwW__pre\"><code class=\"code-block-module__NOThwW__code\" data-geist-code-block=\"true\"><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C56996182-L1\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C56996182-L2\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">  </span><span class=\"token property\">\"gateway\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C56996182-L3\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">    </span><span class=\"token property\">\"routing\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C56996182-L4\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">      </span><span class=\"token property\">\"planningReasoning\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token string\">\"ZDR requested: 5 attempts → 2 ZDR attempts. ZDR execution order: anthropic(system) → bedrock(system)\"</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C56996182-L5\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">    </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C56996182-L6\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">  </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C56996182-L7\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\"></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></div></div></code></pre>\n    </div>\n    <p class=\"text-center text-copy-14 text-gray-900\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">All of these filters work with the <a href=\"https://vercel.com/docs/ai-sdk\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_self\" data-track=\"true\" data-track-click-name=\"article_link\" data-track-click-value=\"https://vercel.com/docs/ai-sdk\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link no-underline link-module__Q1NRQq__highlight [&amp;_u]:no-underline\">AI SDK</a>, <a href=\"https://vercel.com/docs/ai-gateway/sdks-and-apis\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_self\" data-track=\"true\" data-track-click-name=\"article_link\" data-track-click-value=\"https://vercel.com/docs/ai-gateway/sdks-and-apis\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link no-underline link-module__Q1NRQq__highlight [&amp;_u]:no-underline\">Chat Completions API</a>, <a href=\"https://vercel.com/docs/ai-gateway/sdks-and-apis/responses\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_self\" data-track=\"true\" data-track-click-name=\"article_link\" data-track-click-value=\"https://vercel.com/docs/ai-gateway/sdks-and-apis/responses\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link no-underline link-module__Q1NRQq__highlight [&amp;_u]:no-underline\">Responses API</a>, <a href=\"https://vercel.com/docs/ai-gateway/sdks-and-apis/anthropic-compat\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_self\" data-track=\"true\" data-track-click-name=\"article_link\" data-track-click-value=\"https://vercel.com/docs/ai-gateway/sdks-and-apis/anthropic-compat\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link no-underline link-module__Q1NRQq__highlight [&amp;_u]:no-underline\">Anthropic Messages API</a>, and <a href=\"https://vercel.com/docs/ai-gateway/sdks-and-apis/openresponses\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_self\" data-track=\"true\" data-track-click-name=\"article_link\" data-track-click-value=\"https://vercel.com/docs/ai-gateway/sdks-and-apis/openresponses\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link no-underline link-module__Q1NRQq__highlight [&amp;_u]:no-underline\">OpenResponses API</a>.</p>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">Protecting data no longer requires custom logic in every route. By moving these rules to the gateway, compliance becomes infrastructure instead of application busywork. You get your control back, and your team gets to keep shipping.</p>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\">View the models and providers that support Zero Data Retention and Disallow Prompt Training on the <a href=\"https://vercel.com/ai-gateway/models\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_self\" data-track=\"true\" data-track-click-name=\"article_link\" data-track-click-value=\"https://vercel.com/ai-gateway/models\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link no-underline link-module__Q1NRQq__highlight [&amp;_u]:no-underline\">model subpages</a>. Enable Zero Data Retention in your <a href=\"https://vercel.com/d?title=AI+Gateway+Settings&amp;to=%2F%5Bteam%5D%2F%7E%2Fai-gateway%2Fsettings%5C\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_self\" data-track=\"true\" data-track-click-name=\"article_link\" data-track-click-value=\"https://vercel.com/d?title=AI+Gateway+Settings&amp;to=%2F%5Bteam%5D%2F%7E%2Fai-gateway%2Fsettings%5C\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link no-underline link-module__Q1NRQq__highlight [&amp;_u]:no-underline\">dashboard settings</a> today, or read the <a href=\"https://vercel.com/docs/ai-gateway\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_self\" data-track=\"true\" data-track-click-name=\"article_link\" data-track-click-value=\"https://vercel.com/docs/ai-gateway\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link no-underline link-module__Q1NRQq__highlight [&amp;_u]:no-underline\">documentation</a> for full setup details.</p>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "Vercel AI Gateway 引入了团队级和请求级的零数据留存 (ZDR) 功能以及提示词训练选择退出机制，旨在统一管理跨多个 AI 提供商的数据合规性。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "Vercel AI Gateway 引入了团队级和请求级的零数据留存 (ZDR) 功能以及提示词训练选择退出机制，旨在统一管理跨多个 AI 提供商的数据合规性。",
  "summary": "Vercel 为其 AI Gateway 增强了零数据留存 (ZDR) 功能，旨在简化 OpenAI、Anthropic 和 Google 等不同 AI 提供商之间碎片化数据策略的管理。此次更新为 Pro 和 Enterprise 用户提供了团队级的 ZDR 开关，无需更改代码即可强制执行合规性，同时针对特定敏感任务提供了细粒度的请求级控制。通过将这些控制集成到网关中，Vercel 将数据隐私从手动、逐个请求的配置转变为可扩展的基础设施组件，并配有响应元数据中的审计追踪，以验证路由决策。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "跨多个 AI 提供商的集中式 ZDR 执行。",
      "explanation": "AI Gateway 通过自动将流量路由至支持预协商零数据留存协议的 OpenAI、Anthropic 和 Google 模型，抽象化了各个提供商条款的复杂性。"
    },
    {
      "point": "无需修改代码的团队级合规性。",
      "explanation": "Pro 和 Enterprise 团队可以在仪表板中启用全局开关，确保所有外发 AI 请求都遵守严格的数据留存策略，防止开发者意外导致数据泄露。"
    },
    {
      "point": "针对敏感工作流的细粒度请求级控制。",
      "explanation": "开发者可以使用 Vercel AI SDK 以编程方式为特定 API 调用启用 ZDR 或选择退出提示词训练，从而根据具体用例实现灵活的数据敏感度处理方法。"
    },
    {
      "point": "通过响应元数据实现透明的审计追踪。",
      "explanation": "每个 API 响应都包含路由详情，明确了根据请求的合规性过滤器考虑和过滤了哪些提供商，为安全团队提供了清晰的审计日志。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "通过将这些规则移至网关，合规性变成了基础设施，而不是应用程序的繁琐工作。",
    "AI Gateway 确保仅路由至我们已协商过零数据留存协议的提供商，从而自动满足您的数据要求。",
    "团队级 ZDR……适用于您团队发出的每一个请求，无需更改代码。",
